For now I make sure I stay away from any courses in Coursera that asks us to do 'Peer Assessment' as we will never get the certificate.  My HR dept will not regard that I have completed the course without the certificate, which is very upsetting as I had spent many hours completing the course. Thanks for looking into the matter urgently.
